s never been realized. But they\\u2019re afraid to take risks, worried about paying the bills and don\\u2019t know where to begin.<\\/p><p><em>Dream Year <\\/em>was written to help you make the leap from a job you hate to a life you love. You\'ll not only rediscover a life-long dream that got lost along the way, but also learn the process to make it a reality. By combining practical lessons, proven principles and true stories, <em>Dream Year <\\/em>will help you reclaim your passion and find a way to make it your livelihood.<\\/p><p>Let the adventure begin.<\\/p>\",\"22\":[{\"col1\":\"Daring to Dream\",\"col2\":\"Most people know what their dream is; they\'re just too afraid to say it. Naming a dream invokes the forces of fear and insecurity. But you can do this. You\'re supposed to do it. That\\u2019s why the dream was given to you in the first place.\"},{\"col1\":\"Defining the Dream\",\"col2\":\"Every dream has a history. It didn\\u2019t begin just now. You can see traces of it all the way back to your childhood. Pursuing a dream is the culmination of every experience, talent and circumstance you\'ve ever had. No moment has been wasted.\"},{\"col1\":\"Your Idea Model\",\"col2\":\"It\\u2019s not enough to have a great idea. The world is filled with them. What you need is a great idea model - a concept that people have never experienced before. It reinvents the industry, removes the competition and offers a unique experience to the world.\"},{\"col1\":\"Your Financial Model\",\"col2\":\"A great idea is a spreadsheet with skin on. No dream can be sustained without a profitable financial model. And make no mistake \\u2013 whether you\'re profit or non-profit \\u2013 the goal is to make a profit. Otherwise, it\\u2019s not a dream; it\\u2019s a hobby.\"},{\"col1\":\"Executing the Dream\",\"col2\":\"Every dreamer is made up of two people \\u2013 \\u201cordinary you\\u201d and \\u201cCEO you.\\u201d In order to bring your dream to life, \\u201cCEO you\\u201d must be in charge. From 30,000 feet, creating looks like art. From ground level, it\\u2019s a to-do list.\"},{\"col1\":\"The Big Ask\",\"col2\":\"You can\'t delegate the task of creating revenue. No one will care as much as you. Revenue comes from making asks. And making asks comes from building high-trust relationships. Your job is to be a maker of friends.    \"},{\"col1\":\"Branding the Dream\",\"col2\":\"Branding is more than just design. It\\u2019s the quality of your product, the texture of your paper, the look of your photos and how you answer the phone. Branding is about the total user experience. And a great dream requires great branding. \"},{\"col1\":\"Building a Platform \",\"col2\":\"Nobody cares about your idea. There are too many brands, books, companies and causes vying for people\\u2019s attention. It\\u2019s the way of the social economy. By building a platform, you\'re creating a community of people who care.\"},{\"col1\":\"Marketing the Dream\",\"col2\":\"Marketing is about creating demand for your dream. Otherwise, you\\u2019re forced to sell your ideas through persuasion and incentives. Instead of going into sales, create a property that excites people and builds demand for what you do.\"},{\"col1\":\"Growing the Business\",\"col2\":\"Launching a dream requires learning from your mistakes until you get it right. It\\u2019s like trying to open a combination lock when you don\\u2019t know the numbers. You have to turn the tumblers one by one until you finally crack the code.\"},{\"col1\":\"Sustaining the Dream\",\"col2\":\"Most people don\'t quit because of failure. They quit because of discouragement, fear, worry and close-calls. So don\'t quit. Grow in your emotional fortitude. You\'ll be surprised to learn how close you are to success.\"}],\"1\":\"About\",\"14\":[{\"id\":\"28\",\"enabled\":1,\"archived\":\"0\",\"locale\":\"en_us\",\"uri\":null,\"dateCreated\":\"2014-03-29 02:28:52\",\"dateUpdated\":\"2014-03-29 02:30:08\",\"fieldId\":\"14\",\"ownerId\":\"